properties.nuget.description:
Provides classes for performing date calculations using specific calendars, including the Gregorian, Julian, Hijri and Korean calendars.
Commonly Used Types: System.Globalization.HijriCalendar System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar System.Globalization.HebrewCalendar System.Globalization.KoreanCalendar System.Globalization.ThaiBuddhistCalendar System.Globalization.TaiwanCalendar System.Globalization.JapaneseCalendar System.Globalization.GregorianCalendarTypes System.Globalization.PersianCalendar System.Globalization.UmAlQuraCalendar
When using NuGet 3.x this package requires at least version 3.4.
properties.nuget.title: System.Globalization.Calendars
